30
00:01:29,222 --> 00:01:30,321
Junko, please stay back.

31
00:01:30,322 --> 00:01:32,621
And please contact the police right away.

32
00:01:32,622 --> 00:01:33,722
All right.

33
00:01:35,122 --> 00:01:36,422
Mr. Kitagami?

34
00:01:37,822 --> 00:01:39,821
Do you know him?

35
00:01:39,822 --> 00:01:43,221
Yes. He lives next door to me.

36
00:01:43,222 --> 00:01:45,522
Mr. Mouri. How's Mr. Kitagami?

37
00:01:46,822 --> 00:01:48,321
From the looks of it,

38
00:01:48,322 --> 00:01:49,822
he's already...

