00:02:05,822 --> 00:02:07,921
Even heaven is watching the labyrinths of the world.

40
00:02:07,922 --> 00:02:10,121
Full throttle reasoning skills penetrate all mysteries.

41
00:02:10,122 --> 00:02:12,021
While discussing theft prevention,

42
00:02:12,022 --> 00:02:14,321
the neighbor experiences a strange fall.

43
00:02:14,322 --> 00:02:16,021
He sees through the one and only truth.

44
00:02:16,022 --> 00:02:18,321
A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

45
00:02:18,322 --> 00:02:20,822
His name is Detective Conan!

46
00:03:49,381 --> 00:03:54,481
"Security System Pitfall"

47
00:03:57,981 --> 00:04:00,580
"Naotsugu Kitagami (32)" -The victim is Mr. Naotsugu Kitagami,

48
00:04:00,581 --> 00:04:02,080
"Company Employee" -age 32.

49
00:04:02,081 --> 00:04:06,180
He's a company worker who lives in room 704 of this condo.

50
00:04:06,181 --> 00:04:08,780
The cause of his death is most likely brain contusion

51
00:04:08,781 --> 00:04:12,080
caused by a strong blow to his head.

52
00:04:12,081 --> 00:04:15,680
There were many scratches on the front part of the body,

53
00:04:15,681 --> 00:04:16,681
so most likely...

54
00:04:16,682 --> 00:04:19,281
He most likely fell to his death.

55
00:04:20,281 --> 00:04:21,380
Mr. Mouri.

56
00:04:21,381 --> 00:04:24,880
His body smells of alcohol.

57
00:04:24,881 --> 00:04:26,180
I think he got wasted,

58
00:04:26,181 --> 00:04:30,580
slipped on the veranda and fell over the railing.

59
00:04:30,581 --> 00:04:31,881
Pops.

60
00:04:32,881 --> 00:04:37,480
There's a weird smell mixed in with the smell of alcohol.

61
00:04:37,481 --> 00:04:39,180
He smells kind of like peppers.

62
00:04:39,181 --> 00:04:42,580
Never mind, just stay with Junko, will you?

63
00:04:42,581 --> 00:04:43,680
Okay.

64
00:04:43,681 --> 00:04:46,380
Come to think of it, the girl that was with you, who is she?

65
00:04:46,381 --> 00:04:47,580
Well...

66
00:04:47,581 --> 00:04:50,080
We're not in any sort of intimate relationship.

67
00:04:50,081 --> 00:04:52,980
That's not my question.

68
00:04:52,981 --> 00:04:55,180
She's one of the victims of the burglaries

69
00:04:55,181 --> 00:04:57,580
