70
00:04:57,581 --> 00:05:00,980
She called me to discuss this problem,

71
00:05:00,981 --> 00:05:03,380
so I came and ended seeing this incident.

72
00:05:03,381 --> 00:05:04,580
It turned out that she coincidentally

73
00:05:04,581 --> 00:05:08,680
happened to live next door to the victim, Mr. Kitagami.

74
00:05:08,681 --> 00:05:10,280
I see.

75
00:05:10,281 --> 00:05:12,980
Inspector, I think we should start heading over to the room of the victim.

76
00:05:12,981 --> 00:05:14,480
Right.

77
00:05:14,481 --> 00:05:17,580
Go get the manager of the condo then.

78
00:05:17,581 --> 00:05:18,680
Yes, sir.

79
00:05:18,681 --> 00:05:20,280
Officer Chiba!

80
00:05:20,281 --> 00:05:22,480
We're going up to the victim's room!

81
00:05:22,481 --> 00:05:23,581
Yes, sir!

82
00:05:30,681 --> 00:05:31,981
This way please.

83
00:05:33,681 --> 00:05:35,880
