95
00:06:15,181 --> 00:06:16,481
Inspector Megure.

96
00:06:17,481 --> 00:06:19,681
There are liquor bottles on the veranda too.

97
00:06:21,881 --> 00:06:25,080
I guess it's just as I deduced.

98
00:06:25,081 --> 00:06:27,980
But, why did the victim come out to the veranda?

99
00:06:27,981 --> 00:06:32,580
I guess he wanted to cool down his body that got hot.

100
00:06:32,581 --> 00:06:33,980
And...

101
00:06:33,981 --> 00:06:35,680
