And fell upside to the ground.

104
00:06:43,181 --> 00:06:45,481
I see.

105
00:06:51,981 --> 00:06:54,180
Officer Takagi and Chiba.

106
00:06:54,181 --> 00:06:56,180
Just in case, can you two split up

107
00:06:56,181 --> 00:06:58,980
