108
00:06:58,981 --> 00:07:00,181
-Yes, sir! -Yes, sir!

109
00:07:02,281 --> 00:07:04,781
Thank you for your cooperation.

110
00:07:07,181 --> 00:07:10,480
"Sawada"

111
00:07:10,481 --> 00:07:11,580
Yes.

112
00:07:11,581 --> 00:07:14,180
Excuse me, I'm from the police,

113
00:07:14,181 --> 00:07:16,980
could I ask you some questions?

114
00:07:16,981 --> 00:07:18,381
Please wait for a while.

115
00:07:20,681 --> 00:07:22,780
I'm sorry to be intruding on you.

116
00:07:22,781 --> 00:07:24,080
"Ryosuke Sawada (30)" -I thought something was noisy

117
00:07:24,081 --> 00:07:26,080
"Ryosuke Sawada (30)" -below in the parking lot.

118
00:07:26,081 --> 00:07:27,680
Is something wrong?

119
00:07:27,681 --> 00:07:31,880
Do you know Mr. Naotsugu Kitagami of Room 704?

120
00:07:31,881 --> 00:07:34,180
Yes, I know at least what he looks like.

121
00:07:34,181 --> 00:07:39,580
Mr. Kitagami was found dead in the parking lot.

122
00:07:39,581 --> 00:07:40,980
Seriously?

123
00:07:40,981 --> 00:07:43,380
Do you know something?

124
00:07:43,381 --> 00:07:46,080
I stayed home all day today

125
00:07:46,081 --> 00:07:48,280
