181
00:10:51,993 --> 00:10:55,392
Thank you.

182
00:10:55,393 --> 00:10:56,793
Have a good day, then.

183
00:10:58,893 --> 00:11:02,192
What an unexpected conclusion, don't you think?

184
00:11:02,193 --> 00:11:03,992
That the person who happened to fall to his death

185
00:11:03,993 --> 00:11:05,792
was coincidentally a burglar.

186
00:11:05,793 --> 00:11:07,192
I guess so.

187
00:11:07,193 --> 00:11:10,192
All that's left is how do we prove it.

188
00:11:10,193 --> 00:11:13,692
What're you doing, Mr. Mouri?

189
00:11:13,693 --> 00:11:15,493
Well, I was just...

190
00:11:16,493 --> 00:11:18,392
I was looking at my own reflection

191
00:11:18,393 --> 00:11:20,693
