192
00:11:21,693 --> 00:11:25,692
This wall sure is shiny like a mirror.

193
00:11:25,693 --> 00:11:29,892
That's because it's UV coated.

194
00:11:29,893 --> 00:11:32,092
It's quick trying and glossy,

195
00:11:32,093 --> 00:11:34,993
