196
00:11:38,993 --> 00:11:41,692
What's the matter, Conan?

197
00:11:41,693 --> 00:11:45,892
Maybe I dropped the detective badge...

198
00:11:45,893 --> 00:11:47,692
I had in my pocket.

199
00:11:47,693 --> 00:11:51,292
Do you have an idea where you dropped it?

200
00:11:51,293 --> 00:11:52,293
Well...

201
00:11:53,793 --> 00:11:57,792
I think I dropped it in Room 604, Mr. Sawada's room.

202
00:11:57,793 --> 00:11:59,492
May I go get it?

203
00:11:59,493 --> 00:12:00,593
Of course.

204
00:12:05,693 --> 00:12:08,592
What's up? Go and get quick.

205
00:12:08,593 --> 00:12:11,392
Aren't you coming with me, Pops?

206
00:12:11,393 --> 00:12:14,592
Why do I have to go with you?

207
00:12:14,593 --> 00:12:16,793
I don't want to go alone.

208
00:12:17,793 --> 00:12:21,392
You always go everywhere on your own.

209
00:12:21,393 --> 00:12:23,592
What's the problem, Mr. Mouri?

210
00:12:23,593 --> 00:12:25,892
Just go along with him.

211
00:12:25,893 --> 00:12:27,992
Gosh, come on let's go!

212
00:12:27,993 --> 00:12:29,593
Thanks, Pops.

213
00:12:30,593 --> 00:12:32,092
"Sawada"

214
00:12:32,093 --> 00:12:33,292
I'm so sorry.

215
00:12:33,293 --> 00:12:34,792
It's okay,

216
00:12:34,793 --> 00:12:36,392
but once you find what you're looking for,

217
00:12:36,393 --> 00:12:38,392
leave right away, will you?

218
00:12:38,393 --> 00:12:40,992
Yes, of course.

219
00:12:40,993 --> 00:12:43,392
Hey, did you find what you're looking for?

220
00:12:43,393 --> 00:12:46,792
Not yet... Strange.

221
00:12:46,793 --> 00:12:48,292
Gosh...

222
00:12:48,293 --> 00:12:49,592
Are you sure you lost it here?

223
00:12:49,593 --> 00:12:50,793
I found it!

224
00:12:52,293 --> 00:12:54,192
Let's go if you found it.

225
00:12:54,193 --> 00:12:55,193
Okay.

226
00:12:55,194 --> 00:12:56,892
The door's that way.

227
00:12:56,893 --> 00:12:59,293
We're sorry to have intruded on you.

228
00:13:06,593 --> 00:13:07,692
Hey, hey.

229
00:13:07,693 --> 00:13:09,392
What kind of joke is this?

230
00:13:09,393 --> 00:13:10,592
Hey!

231
00:13:10,593 --> 00:13:12,393
