232
00:13:14,693 --> 00:13:15,693
Yes.

233
00:13:17,293 --> 00:13:18,992
Detectives...

234
00:13:18,993 --> 00:13:20,392
Excuse me.

235
00:13:20,393 --> 00:13:24,892
Mr. Mouri asked us to come up here.

236
00:13:24,893 --> 00:13:26,492
Good timing.

237
00:13:26,493 --> 00:13:28,893
Will you do something about him?

238
00:13:30,893 --> 00:13:34,892
Mr. Mouri, what are you doing in his room?

239
00:13:34,893 --> 00:13:36,192
I'm sorry.

240
00:13:36,193 --> 00:13:39,092
I fell asleep while waiting for you to come up.

241
00:13:39,093 --> 00:13:42,392
And? What is it you want?

242
00:13:42,393 --> 00:13:49,092
It bothered me that Mr. Kitagami who was so into security measures

243
00:13:49,093 --> 00:13:50,892
